vice\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"错误率p99从0.0增加到0.65，但与主调用链无关\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**建议**：\n1. 优先解决Redis的延迟问题。\n2. 检查aiops-k8s-05节点的内存使用情况，确保不影响其他关键服务。\n3. 监控AdService的错误率，确认是否为独立问题。", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "5b520645-141", "component": "redis", "reason": "HGET operation latency spike (1.74s to 15.88s, 9.13x increase) causing rrt_max propagation through Redis→CartService→CheckoutService→Frontend call chain", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "TraceAnalysis(5b520645-141)", "observation": "HGET operation latency increased from 1.74s to 15.88s (9.13x) at Redis level"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(cartservice)", "observation": "cartservice-1 rrt_max p99 increased 193% from 80.6s to 4491.8s due to Redis dependency"}, {"step": 3, "action": "CheckNodePodMapping()", "observation": "Redis-cart-0 located on aiops-k8s-08, cartservice-1 on aiops-k8s-05 with memory usage 73.67%"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
